data.title: Eyemart Express Now Open in Avon!
data.text: Now open in Avon—get an eye exam, choose frames, and have your glasses in hand with free same-day speed—all in one place, all in one day. At Eyemart Express, we help people see clearly faster with convenient and affordable eye care that can be completed start-to-finish—from comprehensive eye exams to finished glasses—all in one place, all in one day. We partner with professional eye doctors to provide hassle-free, comprehensive eye exams next door. With an average Google rating of 4.8, our associates provide friendly service to help adults and kids select from more than 2,000 high-quality and affordable frames from brands such as Ray-Ban, Coach, Versace, and Paw Patrol. Our highly skilled in-store lab techs can deliver quality glasses with free same-day speed—over 80% of glasses are finished in one hour. We look forward to helping you and your family see better with our fastest glasses!
